name: Aaron Jardenil
description: Former Philadelphia police officer who works for Gus—and, on occasion, Saul—as a private investigator, head of security, cleaner, and hit man.

name: Christian Asturiano
description: Overqualified high school chemistry teacher from Albuquerque, New Mexico.

name: Kyle Francisco
description: Sleazy and unscrupulous lawyer who acts as Walter and Jesse's attorney and provides some of the series' comic relief.

name: Samuel Cheng
description: former chemist, manufacturer, and distributor who worked in Albuquerque, New Mexico, currently residing in Haines, Alaska.

name: Rafael Calalang
description: Walt and Skyler's brother-in-law and Marie's husband, who works as a U.S. Drug Enforcement Administration (DEA) agent.
